dct_description_sm: New Jersey Geological Survey. United States. Geological Survey. U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey. Alternate title: Princeton, NJ. On upper margin: "Basic map for regional plan prepared with corrections for the Regional Planning Federation of the Philadelphia Tristate District, 1928". Relief shown by 10 feet countour interval and spot elevation. Surveyed in 1885. Cultured revised 1904.
